'''Deck 106''' was the 106th level of the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|first Death Star]]. It contained the [[Death Star Library]] at [[Sector N-One/Legends|Sector N-One]]. It was destroyed along with the rest of the Death Star during the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]] in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]].

